			   README file for

			    ptouch-driver

This is ptouch-driver, a printer driver based on CUPS and foomatic,
for the Brother P-touch label printer family.

See the file `INSTALL' for directions on how to install this software.

After installing, you will probably have to reload or restart CUPS.

This package contains the following directories:

  .        raster filter (rastertoptouch.c)
  driver   foomatic driver XML files
  opt      foomatic options XML files
  printer  foomatic printer XML files

Please note: This software is not in any way related to Brother
Industries, Ltd., except that it is intended for use with their
products.  Any comments to this software should NOT be directed to
Brother Industries, Ltd.

